messages.subject: Re: [Unschooling-dotcom] Still standing
messages.msgSnippet: There are 568 members of this list. Most are still standing. Many are not Americans. Many are lurkers by choice and don t WANT others getting to know them.
messages.messageBody:
There are 568 members of this list.
Most are still standing.
Many are not Americans.
Many are lurkers by choice and don't WANT others getting to know them.
Most want to read about unschooling.
Few to none want 568 messages that say "still standing."

And more than all this, we may never know whether some on this list are NOT
still standing, or will be unable to homeschool now because of the death of a
family member, so I request this be dropped and we use the list to encourage
homeschoolers to help their children learn peacefully and happily in whatever
country they may live.

Sandra
